Subject: Re: [T2] Backwards voltage conversion 12v to 6 v

The easiest thing would probably be to convert the engine to 12 volt. 
You would have to change the coil, cutoff valve/choke, and 
generator/regulator.... I think that would be it. Lots easier than 
changing every bulb, starter bushing, battery, etc.

Hope this helps,
Dan Dypsky
Ocean City, MD
